name: The Eagle of Courage
description:
"My dearest Lorraine,
   Courage is the magick that turns dreams into reality. 
So long as you keep fighting, I will be there by your side.
Your messenger and beloved guardian; here even when apart.

      In Queer Ecdysis together, forever;
      creating Beauty out of Change,
      and Changeout of Beauty.

-Stay strong and courageous,
 Fran"
